# NETSHOPPING::NET_GAMESERVER_START_SESSION_PENDING

## Summary
Check if the game is waiting for script to call NET_GAMESERVER_START_SESSION and set a slot to be fetched (retrieves the inventory and player balance)

## Returns
* **BOOL**
